snippet.textDisplay: My Dad got into an accident and broke his neck. He walked a 1/4 of a mile to help before my mother found him. That in and of itself was a miracle from God, bc he should’ve immediately been dead, or paralyzed completely. After this situation, he went through surgery, lost all upper body movements. My mother worked, prayed, bathed him, fed him, exercised his hands and arms until he could move again. He now works a full time job, and has a great testimony! My mother destroyed her back taking care of him and now she’s in pain constantly but she said she’d never change a thing.
